Question: Explain to your grandmother how to use her smartphone to find new restaurant in her area.
Answer:
the first thing is unlock your phone by sliding the phone screen. then, find an app called yelp on the home screen. touch it slightly once, and you can see it is opened. find the searching bar at the front of the screen and type "current location" into it. press "search", and then you can see a list of restaurants around you and the comments to which other previous customers gave.